---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
const { cta_url } = Astro.props;
---


<main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 mb-8 mt-12 sm:mt-12 sm:mb-12 sm:px-6 md:mt-32 md:mb-20 xl:mt-23 xl:mb-24">
  <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
    <div class="mb-12 md:max-w-1xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
      <h1
        class="mt-1 text-5xl tracking-tight leading-16 font-extrabold sm:leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl uppercase"
      >
        The Suppressed Education<br class="hidden md:inline" /><span class="underline">by Jasper North</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
        The Suppressed Education by Jasper North uncovers the critical knowledge and controversial topics that schools have chosen to ignore. This revealing guide exposes the hidden truths and forbidden subjects that you were never taught in traditional education.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
        With eye-opening insights and in-depth analysis, Black provides a roadmap to understanding the suppressed information that shapes our world. Whether you're eager to explore the gaps in your education, challenge societal norms, or gain a deeper understanding of important yet overlooked topics, this book offers the tools and knowledge you need to expand your worldview.</p>

      <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
        <b>WARNING: This Book Will Be Removed Soon. Hurry and Get It Now.</b>
      </p>

      <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <div>
          <a
            href={cta_url}
            target="_blank"
            class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base leading-6 rounded-md font-semibold text-white bg-book-theme hover:bg-book-hover focus:outline-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10"
          >
            Get It Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-12 relative sm:max-w-lg sm:mx-auto lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:col-span-4 lg:flex lg:items-center"
    >
      <a class="book-container" href={cta_url}>
        <div class="book">
          <Image
            src="/TheSuppressedEducation.png"
            width={300}
            height={600}
            alt="The Suppressed Education by Jasper North Book Cover"
            format="avif"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>